&lt;li&gt;Project including but not limited to:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Trade modelling and pricing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Market data processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Risk reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scenario analytics tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dev Ops / platform engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
